HEADWORD: Perchloride
<hw>Per*chlo"ride</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>A chloride having a higher proportion of chlorine than any other
chloride of the same substance or series.</def>⟦br⟧
